matrix[NUMBER_OF_TILES_RIGHT][NUMBER_OF_TILES_DOWN]
3 type of tiles:
    -Simple race tile 
    -Obstacle A race tile
    -Obstacle B race tile
3 type of Entity on tile
    -Town
    -Random enemy A
    -Random enemy B 

Interactions:
    Click on enemy
	-Open screen with enemy review and portrait 
	-Option to attack or not
    Click on town
	-Quick town summary and player portrait
	-Player interactions(message, befriend)
	
For developers:
   
    -Rerender every 5 minutes;
    -Movable across the map
